1 SECTION 3. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That, except for a contract for high
2 school sports officials extended by a local school system in accordance with Section 2 of this
3 Act, this Act shall be construed to apply only prospectively and may not be applied or
4 interpreted to have any effect on or application to any procurement contracts for high school
5 sports officiating services, as defined in § 4–147 of the Education Article, as enacted under
6 Section 1 of this Act, entered into before the effective date of this Act.
7 SECTION 4. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect July
8 1, 2025.
